import React from "react";
import ParentComponentA from "./HOC/ParentComponentA";

const App=()=> {
  return (
    <>
     <ParentComponentA></ParentComponentA>
    </>
  );
}
export default App;


import React from 'react'
import SharedListComponent from './SharedListComponent'

const ParentComponentA = () => {
    const dataA=[
        {
            id:1,
            name:"apple",
            price:100,
            image_url : "data:image/jpeg;base64,"
        },
        {
            id:2,
            name:"orange",
            price:150,
            image_url:"data:image/jpeg;base64,"
        },
        {
            id:1,
            name:"apple",
            price:100,
            image_url : "data:image/jpeg;base64,"
        },
        {
            id:2,
            name:"orange",
            price:150,
            image_url:"data:image/jpeg;base64,"
        }
    ]
  return (
    <div>
        <center>
      <h3 style={{marginTop:"100px"}}>Parent Component A</h3>
      </center>
      <SharedListComponent data={dataA} />
    </div>
  )

export default ParentComponentA



import React from 'react';

const SharedListComponent = ({data}) => {
  return (
    <div>
      
      <h3 style={{marginLeft:'600px'}}>Shared List Component</h3>
      <ul style={{display:'flex',justifyContent:'space-around'}}>
        {data.map((item)=>(
            <li key={item.id}>
                <p>Item Name : {item.name}</p>
                <img src={item.image_url} height={100} alt="no photo"></img>
                <p>Item Price : {item.price}</p>
            </li>

            
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  )
}

export default SharedListComponent
